summary: A model for a spear made in Cinema 4d r13
descriptionHtml:
I thought i would try a hand a modeling but after a hour of makings this i realized that i could not give this model textures ( for no skills with Photoshop ) and no skills in animation. So i present you with this model and maybe someone else can use it for a cool weapon mod in skyrim and if you do decide to use it please leave me some credit and when you make the mod let me know :P if you dont mind.
I used Cinema 4D R13 to model this and will not supply any other formats for this file/model. 
No textures come with this model.
author: FatCat101
